function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	--Bool for Yorin Comment locked
	bTombEntered = true

	--Set up Markers linked to Trigger
	tDoors = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "Doors")
	idMainDoor = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "MainDoor")[1]
	idRuneStone01 = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "RuneHole01")[1]
	idRuneStone02 = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "RuneHole02")[1]
	locDoor = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "DoorLoc")[1]
	idYorinInvest = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "Yorin")[1]
	idRetreat01 = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "Retreat")[1]
	
	-- always refresh variable
	followerYorin = idActor
	
	--Yorin moves to the Warded Passage and investigates
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerYorin) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(followerYorin, false)
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerYorin)
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CON_CALL_LOCK_01, followerYorin)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerYorin, locDoor, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerYorin, locDoor)
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(followerYorin, CON_CALL_LOCK_01)
		Hydra.QActorSheath(followerYorin)
		Hydra.QActorWait(followerYorin, 1)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(followerYorin)
		Hydra.ActorDelete(followerYorin)
	end
	
	--Enable static Yorin, inspecting Runed Passageway
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idYorinInvest)
	Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(idYorinInvest, "NPC_Yorin_Idle_Stand_Inspect_EyeLevel")
	
	Hydra.EventSend("DoorInvest")

end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	--Disembodied Spirits see Yorin as a Pale Knight; enemy
	local tPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
	
	for i, idPlayer in ipairs(tPlayers) do
		if Hydra.ActorsInSameWorld(idPlayer, idActorNPC) then
			Hydra.ActorPlayDisembodiedConversation(CON_DISEMBODIED_REVENGE, idPlayer)
		end
	end

	--Activate spirit effects on Cairns
	for i, idCairns in pairs(tCairns) do
		Hydra.ActorDelete(idCairns)
	end
	
	for i, tSummoning in pairs(tSummoning) do
		Hydra.ActorEnable(tSummoning)
	end
	
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	--Yorin pleads with the Spirits
	Hydra.QActorPower(idYorinTomb, "AnimKey_Emote_Talk_Pleading")
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CON_YORIN_PLEADING, idYorinTomb)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idYorinTomb, CON_YORIN_PLEADING)
	
	-- Safety measure.  If player leaves area during theater, conversation finished will never fire on Yorin and 
	-- will block progression but QEmpty will fire and it's always valid for the quest to send an event.
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idYorinTomb)
	Hydra.EventSend("PaleRevenge02_Finished")

end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	
	--Spawn Vengeful Wildwood
	--Destroy protected cairns
	for i, idSummoner in pairs(tSummoning) do
		Hydra.ActorDelete(idSummoner)
	end
	
	--Enable Vengeful Wildwood 
	for i, idWoodWraiths in pairs(tWoodWraiths) do
		Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idWoodWraiths, 4.0)
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idWoodWraiths, FXKIT_SPIRIT_BURST)
		Hydra.ActorEnable(idWoodWraiths)
	end
	

end
